  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate the clinical effect of rapamycin combined with TACE on early-stage HCC with
      overexpression of ASPH after radical surgery using randomized controlled study and provide a
      new anti-recurrence treatment for HCC patients after operation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
